  encounterName: Mysterious Offer
  description: "As night falls, a cloaked figure appears from nowhere and joins your
    campfire. The figure has no face. When you look at it, all you see is absolute
    darkness. However their voice is smooth as silk: \u201CI can give you what you
    desperately lack. Supplies, riches, or tools \u2014 take your pick. But everything
    comes at a price\u2026 one you will pay when the journey nears its end.\u201D"
  biome: -1
  depth: 0
  dangerLevel: 0
  isUnique: 0
  choices:
  - choiceDescription: Ask for supplies.
    resultText: "You reach out, and sacks of grain and water jars appear from thin
      air. The figure bows slightly. \u201CYour hunger will not trouble you again
      \u2014 until we meet once more.\u201D"
    risky: 0
    suppliesOutcome: 100
    peopleOutcome: 0
