  - choiceDescription: Ask for valuables.
    resultText: 'The cloaked figure flicks his hand, and a chest of gold and jewels
      clatters at your feet. His smile is the last thing you see before the figure
      melts into the shadows. '
    risky: 0
    suppliesOutcome: 0
    peopleOutcome: 0
    valuablesOutcome: 40
    gearOutcome: 0
    typeOfPrerequisites: 0
    luckOutcome: 0
    fogOfWarOutcome: 0
    impendingDoomOutcome: 0
    addDebt: 1
  - choiceDescription: Ask for gear.
    resultText: "Your blades sharpen and glow in the dark, ropes mend themselves,
      and new tools appear among your cargo. The figure whispers: \u201CMay they
      serve you well\u2026 for a time.\u201D"
    risky: 0
    suppliesOutcome: 0
    peopleOutcome: 0
    valuablesOutcome: 0
    gearOutcome: 40
    typeOfPrerequisites: 0
    luckOutcome: 0
    fogOfWarOutcome: 0
    impendingDoomOutcome: 0
    addDebt: 1
  - choiceDescription: Refuse the offer
    resultText: 'The moment you refuse, the cloaked silhouette disappears in the
      blink of the eye. As if the figure was never here. Maybe it was never here.

